WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.985 --> 00:00:04.968
♪♪

2
00:00:29.265 --> 00:00:31.890
KIRI
Dad, I know you think I'm crazy.

3
00:00:36.334 --> 00:00:37.663
But I feel her.

4
00:00:43.568 --> 00:00:45.062
I hear her heart beat.

5
00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:49.440
She's so close.

6
00:00:57.271 --> 00:00:59.492
JAKE SULLY
So what does her heartbeat sound like?

7
00:01:06.296 --> 00:01:07.926
KIRI
Mighty.

8
00:01:07.977 --> 00:01:09.553
♪♪

9
00:01:17.327 --> 00:01:18.562
NA'VI
Woo!

10
00:01:26.194 --> 00:01:29.231
TONOWARI
We cannot let you bring your war here.

11
00:01:30.059 --> 00:01:32.284
LO'AK
Outcast, that's all they see.

12
00:01:33.981 --> 00:01:34.990
TSIREYA
I see you.

13
00:01:36.372 --> 00:01:37.372
♪♪

14
00:01:40.985 --> 00:01:43.454
LO'AK
The Way of Water connects all things.

15
00:01:45.746 --> 00:01:46.991
Before your birth...

16
00:01:48.796 --> 00:01:50.260
...and after your death.

17
00:01:52.829 --> 00:01:54.131
NEYTIRI
This is our home!

18
00:01:56.449 --> 00:01:58.744
JAKE SULLY
I need you with me.

19
00:01:59.590 --> 00:02:01.221
And I need you to be strong.

20
00:02:09.613 --> 00:02:11.523
Strong heart.

